{"tid":1944281,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"連登 燈死埋wiki...","createTime":"2020-03-26T09:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T11:07:51.000Z","uid":10757,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"dab9059afa830b8ea95ed5edb376f4d35850dfed","tid":1944281,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:32:48.000Z","msg":"香港電視去年淨虧損擴大至近2.9億元<br />\n<br />\n香港電視公布，去年淨虧損近2.9億元，按年擴大近1.2倍，不派末期息。期內，經調整後的扣除利息、稅項、折舊及攤銷前虧損2.16億元，按年減少20%。去年營業額增加近58%至14.1億元，當中來自直接商品銷售11.01億元，按年升近61%；特許銷售收入及其他服務收入近3.03億元，按年升53%；廣告收入淨額及節目版權1020萬元，按年跌22%。"},{"pid":"39069350f8baffdb3dd962a8c6ad66d6932fbd99","tid":1944281,"uid":44916,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:34:27.000Z","msg":"𣎴嬲都蝕住做"},{"pid":"fd7a9e4bc17b814afd22f51b640b8782ddeb8c06","tid":1944281,"uid":114467,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:34:49.000Z","msg":"截至二零一九年十二月三十一日止年度之全年業績"},{"pid":"339e4e2795c6ecd5f9893c93f1db0ec28a0c0387","tid":1944281,"uid":123696,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"今年無賺到笑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7b112e0c03bd9fa978af163bbbdd4b114ab36f","tid":1944281,"uid":4258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"去年營業額增加近58%至14.1億元，當中來自直接商品銷售11.01億元，按年升近61%；特許銷售收入及其他服務收入近3.03億元，按年升53%<br />\n<br />\n利好，升"},{"pid":"79c748571753668abbf512563a5d3c1ba8d444a1","tid":1944281,"uid":99885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"本身死緊 點燈死"},{"pid":"c7ff5763b2a7d710af8bcfbfe46f6efb71f55802","tid":1944281,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"339e4e2795c6ecd5f9893c93f1db0ec28a0c0387","tid":1944281,"uid":123696,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"今年無賺到笑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"